description: The MSCI World Sector Neutral Quality Index (USD) (TRN) aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large and mid-cap companies from global developed markets with high Quality scores Weighted dependant on Quality characteristics such as Return-on-equity, leverage and earning variability Reviewed on a semi annual basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.msci.com
name: Xtrackers MSCI World Quality UCITS ETF 1C
